  "key": "C# major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "I see it in your eyes, I see it in your ears Since we're gonna be not in the place we should Is it regret or is it what we should do to just stop and breathe? Are we coming down or are we trying to be founded? That illuminates around me, yeah, illuminated, not here Are we united? Are you united? Cause everything goes, everything goes Broken promises are never kept, I'm just trying to be there When the moon continues, shining oh so bright Lighting up the darkness, bask in the afterglow When you know that you've lost, and it's just there Watching all of the blood on the walls, you're basking in the afterglow What you gonna do, what you gonna be? Some people will tell you when you're small, you'll see that Don't think too much about that, roll your life in round 9 Don't roll in your dread, don't roll in your crime Don't be like benign, be free at all times Be cautious to the ones that take you away from you When the moon is shining, light me up in that dark I need you to bask in the afterglow When the thing is just, it's pulling you apart There's nowhere to turn, you're just basking in the afterglow When all the lines go from me to you, and you to them I say go on past it Every time you think of me inside you When the show is just, it gets dark and it's More than you can ever picture, bask in the afterglow And your heart is just, something's settled there It's not what you wanted, but it's what you needed Know that's afterglow inside it, the afterglow beyond it Silver lining guides your heart to start a fire of thunder If you're not dead, you're still here baby You're roaming in the afterglow Afterglow, that's right, me and you, together, dude, chick That's how we roll That's how we roll I got it, I'm telling you that Don't lose hope, kitty cat And you may have our space bar And another R",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 20.079999923706055,
      "text": "I see it in your eyes, I see it in your ears",
      "start": 15.359999656677246
    },
    {
      "end": 24.420000076293945,
      "text": "Since we're gonna be not in the place we should",
      "start": 20.079999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 31.81999969482422,
      "text": "Is it regret or is it what we should do to just stop and breathe?",
      "start": 24.420000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 37.18000030517578,
      "text": "Are we coming down or are we trying to be founded?",
      "start": 33.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 41.86000061035156,
      "text": "That illuminates around me, yeah, illuminated, not here",
      "start": 37.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 46.2599983215332,
      "text": "Are we united? Are you united?",
      "start": 42.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 50.68000030517578,
      "text": "Cause everything goes, everything goes",
      "start": 46.5
    },
    {
      "end": 55.7400016784668,
      "text": "Broken promises are never kept, I'm just trying to be there",
      "start": 50.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 60.220001220703125,
      "text": "When the moon continues, shining oh so bright",
      "start": 55.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 64.68000030517578,
      "text": "Lighting up the darkness, bask in the afterglow",
      "start": 60.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 68.69999694824219,
      "text": "When you know that you've lost, and it's just there",
      "start": 64.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 73.80000305175781,
      "text": "Watching all of the blood on the walls, you're basking in the afterglow",
      "start": 68.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 75.69999694824219,
      "text": "What you gonna do, what you gonna be?",
      "start": 73.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 78.22000122070312,
      "text": "Some people will tell you when you're small, you'll see that",
      "start": 76.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 82.76000213623047,
      "text": "Don't think too much about that, roll your life in round 9",
      "start": 78.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 87.19999694824219,
      "text": "Don't roll in your dread, don't roll in your crime",
      "start": 82.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 91.9000015258789,
      "text": "Don't be like benign, be free at all times",
      "start": 87.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 96,
      "text": "Be cautious to the ones that take you away from you",
      "start": 91.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 100.58000183105469,
      "text": "When the moon is shining, light me up in that dark",
      "start": 96.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 105,
      "text": "I need you to bask in the afterglow",
      "start": 100.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 109.16000366210938,
      "text": "When the thing is just, it's pulling you apart",
      "start": 105
    },
    {
      "end": 113.80000305175781,
      "text": "There's nowhere to turn, you're just basking in the afterglow",
      "start": 109.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 122.19999694824219,
      "text": "When all the lines go from me to you, and you to them",
      "start": 113.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 127.83999633789062,
      "text": "I say go on past it",
      "start": 122.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 132.0800018310547,
      "text": "Every time you think of me inside you",
      "start": 128.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 136.0800018310547,
      "text": "When the show is just, it gets dark and it's",
      "start": 132.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 140.86000061035156,
      "text": "More than you can ever picture, bask in the afterglow",
      "start": 136.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 145.3000030517578,
      "text": "And your heart is just, something's settled there",
      "start": 141
    },
    {
      "end": 149.27999877929688,
      "text": "It's not what you wanted, but it's what you needed",
      "start": 145.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 154.1999969482422,
      "text": "Know that's afterglow inside it, the afterglow beyond it",
      "start": 149.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 158.5800018310547,
      "text": "Silver lining guides your heart to start a fire of thunder",
      "start": 154.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 164.5800018310547,
      "text": "If you're not dead, you're still here baby",
      "start": 158.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 167.66000366210938,
      "text": "You're roaming in the afterglow",
      "start": 165.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 172.4199981689453,
      "text": "Afterglow, that's right, me and you, together, dude, chick",
      "start": 168.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 174.66000366210938,
      "text": "That's how we roll",
      "start": 172.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 177.66000366210938,
      "text": "That's how we roll",
      "start": 174.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 181.86000061035156,
      "text": "I got it, I'm telling you that",
      "start": 178.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 184.10000610351562,
      "text": "Don't lose hope, kitty cat",
      "start": 181.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 186.83999633789062,
      "text": "And you may have our space bar",
      "start": 185.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 189.0399932861328,
      "text": "And another R",
      "start": 187.8000030517578
    }
  ],
